{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "牌局", "storyInfo": "Outcast來到小丘郡，在羅德島辦事處結識駐軍儀仗兵簡。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "7:11 A.M. 天氣/陰"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島駐小丘郡辦事處"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家早上好！今天天氣真不錯，你說是不是呀，奧利弗叔叔？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你啊，我就說，還有誰會一大早來這裡敲門呢？不過啊，今天明明是個陰天，哪來的天氣不錯？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要不下雨，都是好天氣。這可是在小丘郡。再說了，您怎麼知道過一會不會轉晴呢？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行吧，說不過你。碎紙機，你也別磨磨蹭蹭的了，並沒有客戶上門，只是天天偷懶的小簡妮而已。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧您說的。碎紙機大哥，你也一起過來吧。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天我給你們帶來了大蕉太妃派，還有黃油酥餅。上周爸爸給我寄了點茶葉，我也帶上了。奧利弗叔叔，淡奶還有嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......剩下的早長毛了。他根本就，不記得去買。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是輪到你去買了嗎？難不成我記錯了？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弗雷德！威爾！你們也來說說！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦好啦，為這麼小的事吵架可不值得。瞧，這是什麼？是新鮮的淡奶還有乳酪哦，我路過早市的時候買的，先送給你們啦。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，早就想試試做奶茶喝了，我猜至少奧利弗叔叔會喜歡的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，還是小簡妮最體貼。威爾，我希望你好好學學，至少別長成你旁邊這個代號碎紙機的傢伙一副德行。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這酥餅味道真不錯......對了，薇洛小姐，你天天這麼跑出來給我們送早點，不會被你的長官教訓嗎？", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我記得維多利亞軍隊的規矩，還挺嚴的。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......這個嘛，你們不用擔心。我是儀仗兵啊，沒有重要活動或者徵兵宣傳什麼的，我也派不上用場，士官長平時根本不會想起我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再說了，我也不是一點正事都沒幹呀。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每天早上一起床，我做的第一件事就是把這面旗子從架子上取下來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在等著麵粉發酵和煮咖啡的時候，我會一點一點地把旗幟上的褶皺熨平。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "烤完酥餅，我得沖洗一下身上沾著的麵粉。頭髮自然晾乾需要時間，這正是保養旗杆、讓它像嶄新的一般鋥亮的好時機。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#2$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗叔叔，請先別急著動茶杯——還太燙呢。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個圓滿的早晨，任何一樣東西都要做到光彩照人，這樣才能給自己和各位帶來快樂——這就是我的人生信條。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天的派口味怎樣呀，碎紙機大哥？要不要再來一點？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......完美，和過去每一天一樣。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的嗎？我也嘗嘗......似乎糖多放了一點點。明天我會注意的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以後我可不敢跟著他們一起說你偷懶了，薇洛小姐。", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——簡妮。大家都這麼叫我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，呃......簡小姐。我真怕他們也想讓我早上的日程表變得和你的一樣充實。", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可別誇我啦。我不像各位，我能為這裡的人們做的事情很有限。嗯......我想茶水的溫度可以了，麻煩喝之前先攪拌一下——", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bottlebroken", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你又把球弄飛了，克雷格！", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去撿。", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了......飛屋子裡去了。", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一砸到那些大人就、就壞了啊！上次卡羅爾姐姐不是被......", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "噓，噓......有人出來了，我們快跑！", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是誰弄丟的球呀？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你嗎，小朋友？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克雷格......克雷格快跑啊！球我們不要了......", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行......那個球是爸爸留下的......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太害羞的話會交不到朋友哦。來吧，把手伸出來。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你會打我嗎？", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為什麼要打你呀？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你的衣服髒了。", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，是我自己不小心。沒關係的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些和你一樣的大人，他們從來不管是不是我弄髒的衣服。", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們總是打人。不過他們不用手，他們用腳踢。他們還會尖叫著，讓我們滾遠些。", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那說明他們一定不是你的朋友。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就住在這附近嗎？我好像見過你。你媽媽是不是每天早上天剛亮的時候，就會在附近十七區的小巷子裡賣蘋果？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們家的蘋果味道很好哦。沒那麼脆，但還是很甜，適合做成果泥抹麵包吃。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣吧。姐姐把球放在這窗台上。你待會過來自己拿好不好？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 280.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，慢一些，我的手上還有茶水，都沾到你頭髮上啦。我給你擦擦吧。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 2.0, "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫簡妮。你叫什麼名字呀？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我叫......", "name": "克雷格"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_240", "name2": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克雷格！你媽媽在找你。快、快走吧！", "name": "焦急的孩子A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "外面好像很熱鬧？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是孩子們在玩球。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這群小傢伙，總是一大早就在街上跑來跑去。上回我們的窗戶玻璃碎了一塊，一定也是他們幹的。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......小孩子嘛。我小時候也弄壞過鄰居叔叔家的盆栽，後來被爸爸狠狠教訓了一頓。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你的手碰到那男孩了。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才嗎？是呀，不趕緊擦乾淨的話，他的頭髮會一直黏乎乎的。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他父親去世了，半年前。可憐人，得了礦石病。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很多人，因為這個，不敢碰他。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工人，沒什麼錢。那家異鐵副產品加工廠和安利康，有合作。但預防藥物，他們沒有給足量。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你遲疑，正常。他們社區，有五分之一的家庭裡，都出過礦石病人。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們對彼此都算照顧。如果沒有那些士兵......", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機！你糊塗了。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒關係，您只是陳述事實。我聽說過......我的同僚對礦石病人......不，不光是對病人，他們對這裡的居民都有些誤解。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我不那麼想。大家都是維多利亞人，不是嗎？他們的日子不算好過，我、我都明白。可我希望他們也能過得高興一點。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說......我是不是應該對那孩子更好一些啊？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不要勉強。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼大家都愁眉苦臉的啊？簡小姐，我把撲克拿過來了。你不是說我們可以邊喝茶邊玩撲克嗎？", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。威爾說得對，難得快出太陽了，我們不該浪費這好天氣。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都坐下吧，我給大家再倒點茶，還剩下大半壺呢。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是我又贏了？", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別得意太早，晚上你值班。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？怎麼又是我！", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不懂嗎？這是我們的賭注！誰贏了牌，誰就要負責掃地、整理文件、給大家買下午茶......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_090"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我能悔牌嗎？", "name": "幹員威爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_090"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗叔叔，你的玩笑要讓威爾哭出來啦。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這不就是打牌的樂趣？哈哈哈哈！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小建議——下次換牌的時候，也要記得留意下身後。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼——？！是誰在說話？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$marketplace_intro", "key": "$marketplace_loop", "volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "順便說一聲，茶泡得很不錯。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您、您好！請問您是？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（突然就進了屋，我們誰都沒有發現......）", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都叫我Outcast，美麗的瓦伊凡小姐。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我未經同意就品嘗了你的茶水。看在我趕了這麼遠路的份上，但願你不會太介意。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......您、您隨意。如果您沒吃早飯的話，想嘗嘗我烤的派嗎？可能甜了點......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。很多老朋友都知道，我最愛甜食——尤其是外觀被烤製得如此精巧可愛的維多利亞甜食。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......Outcast女士，謝謝您的鼓勵。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——Outcast。沒什麼人稱我為女士，沒這個必要。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是、是您！我想起來了......威爾！快、快把桌子清乾淨——", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我以為您會晚兩天才到。上次電訊裡說，您才剛進入邊境。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒辦法，我有十年沒來過維多利亞了。一些地方擁擠了起來，另一些地方則和我一樣變得沒那麼新。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是在半島郡搭車的時候走錯了一段路，我昨天就該見到你們了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳，請您諒解，小丘郡這地方不算起眼，我們辦事處不常有精英幹員來。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上回我在米諾斯附近外勤的時候見到了Stormeye先生——那都已經是兩年前的事啦。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "精英幹員 ？光是聽起來就好厲害。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——只是羅德島幹員的不同分工而已。而且，我現在差不多就是個普通的文職人員，這次來小丘郡就是為了取幾份資料。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您太謙虛了。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到資料，您是想先看財務表，還是這半年的進貨出貨庫存明細表......（示意威爾）", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別著急。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事情還不算那麼緊迫，不至於非要讓我這個饑腸轆轆的可憐人馬上投入工作。難得出一趟差，稍微偷一點懶也是合理的吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......我非常理解。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我沒有打擾到你們小小的娛樂活動。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "Outcast隨手拿起一張牌。薄薄的紙片在她的指尖旋轉了三圈半，倏地消失了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "y": 252.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "yTo": 65.0, "duration": 15.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊！剛剛那張牌去了哪裡？", "name": "簡妮"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在這裡。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又變回來了！這是什麼奇妙的空間法術嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個小小的把戲罷了。有個總是陰沉著臉的同事教過我，每當我希望大家把注意力集中到我指尖的時候，這麼做會很有效。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是都放鬆一些了？請坐下，奧利弗，還有碎紙機、威爾，以及站在角落裡的那位年輕人——我記得你叫弗雷德。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放下你手裡的資料夾，和我們一起享受這難得的清閒吧。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "x": 386.0, "y": 222.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "xTo": 170.0, "yTo": 20.0, "duration": 12.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......這樣真的可以嗎？", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是你們更希望我這個一臉疲憊的外鄉人站在這裡變十分鐘無聊的戲法？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，都坐下吧。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們請繼續。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於我，我還想好好品味下這美味的加了淡奶的紅茶和香甜可口的派。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這裡還有更多酥餅，我是說如果您還覺得餓的話......", "name": "簡妮"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這精緻的小甜點讓我空空的腸胃得到了久違的滿足。我的舌頭開始想念一些更激烈的味道了。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這位可愛的小姐——", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我叫簡，簡·薇洛。", "name": "簡妮"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是同樣可愛的名字。你該不會還沒到能喝酒的年齡吧？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早就成年啦，女士......Outcast。我畢竟是一名軍人。", "name": "簡妮"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？那身灰撲撲的維多利亞軍服可完全襯不出你的金髮有多燦爛。奧利弗，你們運氣真好，無論是多陰沉的日子，屋子裡總有陽光。", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScale": 1.7, "yScale": 1.7, "y": 222.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 0.5, "xScaleFrom": 1.7, "yScaleFrom": 1.7, "xScaleTo": 1.4, "yScaleTo": 1.4, "xTo": 170.0, "yTo": 20.0, "duration": 12.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......是這樣沒錯，小簡妮給我們帶來了很多歡笑。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧您說的，奧利弗叔叔，是你們好心接納了總是偷偷溜出軍營的我。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到你們關係如此融洽，我先前還有些小小的驚訝——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，維多利亞士兵要是都像你這麼令人喜愛，那些流傳在大地上的可怕傳說至少能少掉一半。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，我沒理解錯的話，您大概是在誇獎我......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#3$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連來這裡的路上，我也見到了一些不那麼愉快的場面。不過，這並沒有影響到我與你們在這裡相識的喜悅。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能認識您......我也好高興！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，為我們的相逢乾杯？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一趟來得有些匆忙，我只帶了點普通的杜松子酒，按我自己的口味加了過量的檸檬汁，或許對你們來說有些酸——", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們工作時間，不喝酒。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這煞風景的人！", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，是我疏忽了。同為羅德島幹員，我也不能例外，還是一起喝茶吧。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "21_I1", "fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shufflecards", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以——下面該誰開牌？", "name": "Outcast"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是、是我。", "name": "幹員威爾"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "Outcast"}}, 